episodes.title: Jehovah's Witnesses Debutante Movie Destroying lives JW_Untoldtruth # 547
episodes.description: Debutante is a short, contemporary drama set in the world of Irish Jehovah's Witnesses. It's a story of an 18-year-old Meg, who experiences, in a rather severe way, the overbearing religious control practiced by the members of this community. At its heart, it's a film about growing up.

episodes.title: Jehovah's Witnesses and Universal Medicine Cult Documentary  JW_Untoldtruth # 352
episodes.description: The Universal Medicine Cult is an Australian Cult that uses the same techniques to keep unwanted people out of their premises, great investigation from an Australian Investigation channel on this Cult.
